OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, heavy at times in
OL,7,Fthe west. Dry with some bright spells
OL,8,Facross Inverness and Nairn. Breezy
OL,9,Facross the Hebrides.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMainly cloudy with outbreaks
OL,12,Fof rain through the evening and
OL,13,Fovernight, heavy at times in the west.
OL,14,FMainly dry towards the Moray Firth and
OL,15,FSpeyside.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FCloudy with further outbreaks
OL,18,Fof rain in the morning. Becoming drier
OL,19,Fand brighter through the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
