OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry with sunny spells and isolated
OL,7,Fshowers on Tuesday. Dry with sunny
OL,8,Fspells and becoming increasingly warm
OL,9,Fduring Wednesday and Thursday.
